{
  "stem": "26609.10",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But we'll see what will happen to your child.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I went back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I went back to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "In, you could go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But out, not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Some people went out, from the committee.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So they could-- because they communicated with the Germans, they could go out and go into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I went in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They didn't know who I am.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Some non-Jews could get in if they have something-- to deliver something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was at the begin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my sister, my other sister, brother-in-law-- is it you?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No one could believe that I went there to-- thinking I gave up the child to the hospital and came back.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It wasn't like here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You go to a hospital.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You deliver a child to a hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was miles and miles in nighttime in wartime.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said to her, all right, I came to see if you're all alive.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We'll see what will happen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I told them what that sister told me in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then I didn't think of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remembered-- that saved me-- that my younger sister, the one who survived-- I think I told you her story too.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When that Polish woman gave her a document out of a certificate of a church and told her to go to Lublin with it-- and from Lublin, she can somehow go to Germany or let herself to get caught on the street and sent to Germany as a Christian.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She had that paper.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] She begged that Christian-- that woman, the same woman who gave her-- said, look, I have an older sister, older from me.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she said, she's quite good looking.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She doesn't look like Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
